{"tid":2343815,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青年涉6.12金鐘襲警 香淑嫻裁定罪成 判監一個月 警長曾稱為「止暴制亂」並無驗傷","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T15:06:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"446c5018e1c5dd04ea5d07b7f2b9a95cea9a0fe4","tid":2343815,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12460&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=9cb30cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12460</a><br />\n<br />\n#沙田裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#香淑嫻裁判官<br />\n#0612金鐘 #裁決 #襲警<br />\n<br />\n陳 (23)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：襲警<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2019年6月12日在金鐘夏愨道近38555號燈柱襲擊警長430方樂文。<br />\n<br />\n速報：罪名成立🛑<br />\n<br />\n🛑判處監禁一個月🛑"},{"pid":"950525e377e19a45b8d6f9f092cf8bd0a06fd695","tid":2343815,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"無傷襲咩警"},{"pid":"ea4bce55f2a98bcaae1d9578ff66e05332ac65da","tid":2343815,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"警長方樂文憶述，當日以速龍隊員身分當值，在早上7時許，與其他警員在夏慤道近政府總部外設防線時，有近百名示威者在約15米外聚集，其間他看到被告在人群中戴上口罩，遂上前截查。<br />\n<br />\n方樂文稱，截住被告後，面對面捉住被告兩邊上臂，其間被告「手舞足蹈」地掙扎，又多次向警方大叫「黑警、你冇權」，方樂文向其3次發口頭警告，惟被告沒理會，並「用盡全力」雙手推方樂文的胸口，令他「甩手」及「後退一大步」。方樂文隨即箍住被告上半身，並聯同其他警員制服被告。<br />\n<br />\n方樂文又稱，事後一至兩小時曾到政總洗手間檢視傷勢，看到自己胸口有紅印。不過，他在辯方盤問下承認沒有到醫院驗傷，亦沒想到需為傷勢拍照作證據用，因「當時我嘅職責係要繼續當值，止暴制亂」。"},{"pid":"09ffdaca846ba1caf203a65bc6aa9ef989820d10","tid":2343815,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da9f06e141b05a7542c198817af823e7c9a67170","tid":2343815,"uid":331551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"屌, 無驗傷報告, 都可以入罪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e28f58c301462c93fd2d710871bcf51cc9efa","tid":2343815,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"依家黑警講吓就架啦"},{"pid":"785c804a0a7f4ddf0acfb0d1804e9d5ba3cc2f31","tid":2343815,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b21e28f58c301462c93fd2d710871bcf51cc9efa","tid":2343815,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"依家黑警講吓就架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:39:17.000Z","msg":"再一次証明香港無咗法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f208d9614daa74199c711434e4e449e1a82d1e6","tid":2343815,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9095e5e2505e44ee40c529a98e56fd27374c6a20","tid":2343815,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"申請保釋等候上訴獲批✅，條件如下：<br />\n保釋金由兩千元增至一萬元<br />\n每星期到警署報到兩次<br />\n居住在報稱地址<br />\n不得離開香港，需交出旅遊證件"},{"pid":"a8bdd43ecc9ea684b9897b167806a2df47641d77","tid":2343815,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"950525e377e19a45b8d6f9f092cf8bd0a06fd695","tid":2343815,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"無傷襲咩警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"空氣襲警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce63ed0d5c1aed97c68594a6805c1d57e8069d00","tid":2343815,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9095e5e2505e44ee40c529a98e56fd27374c6a20","tid":2343815,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"申請保釋等候上訴獲批✅，條件如下：<br />\n保釋金由兩千元增至一萬元<br />\n每星期到警署報到兩次<br />\n居住在報稱地址<br />\n不得離開香港，需交出旅遊證件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"1萬蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wo